<h1>Edelweiss</h1>

The Edelweiss was the third Serge panel I built and is a clone of the <a href="https://randomsource.net/">Random Source</a> panel of the same name. This was originally created as a DIY build and so I was able to follow the original build documents found on the <a href="https://www.modwiggler.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=108698">Mod Wiggler build thread</a>.

All the PCBs were bought from <a href="https://www.elby-designs.com">Elby Designs</a> with the exception of the power distribution board mentioned in previous builds.

<img class="onpage" src="./images/edelweiss-front.jpg" alt="Edelweiss Front"/>

